<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得去市区。”罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得找出是谁抢劫了运钞车。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看了一眼零食店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还要给朋友们买零食。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回来的时候再买吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，她看见一个男人买走了最后一个椒盐脆饼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！”罗西说，“特勒尔想要椒盐脆饼呢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>算了，现在我有更重要的事情要做！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快罗西到了美罗城市区。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一辆运钞车停在路边上，侧倒着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探正一边跟两名警卫交谈，一边在小本子上写着什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您好！侦探先生！”罗西落到地面后喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您要给这些人开罚单吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你真有意思。”侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不是开罚单，我在记笔记。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着两名警卫。“接下来发生了什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”司机说，“我们当时正在去银行的路上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”另一名警卫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“突然有东西抓住了卡车。”司机说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后卡车就翻了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们下车以后，所有的钱都不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西仔细地看了看那辆卡车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奇怪。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她指着车身的一圈印记说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好像是绳子之类的东西缠住了卡车。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>司机眼睛一亮。“很有可能是绳子！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们翻倒以后，听到有人喊 ‘咦哈’!”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看向另外一名警卫。“记得吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“记得。”另一名警卫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咦哈？”史密斯说，“那是牛仔经常说的话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“应该是的。”司机说，“我们还听到马的声音。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”另一位警卫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西交叉着双臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道是谁抢劫了那辆运钞车。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯显得很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你真的知道了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”罗西说，“是臭巴特！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“臭巴特？那个不守法的牛仔？”侦探说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是美罗城唯一一个不守法的牛仔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探摸着下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是对的，火箭女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小偷一定是臭巴特。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我敢肯定他会抢更多的运钞车。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得阻止他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们首先要找到他。”侦探说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西点点头，看向繁忙的街头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有很多车经过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有大型公交车，还有一辆运钞车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去跟着那辆运钞车。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“臭巴特肯定会来抢，我已经准备好了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>